1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: kern.9,v 1.2 2002/11/08 08:08:47 mpech Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2002 CubeSoft Communications, Inc. <http://www.csoft.org>
